sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: GetBoardConfiguration
    C->>A: GetBoardConfiguration()
    A->>PM: GetBoardConfiguration()
    PM->>PA: GetBoardConfiguration()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(board_config.json) [or DefaultBoardConfiguration()]
    PA-->>PM: *BoardConfiguration
    PM-->>A: *BoardConfiguration
    A->>A: convertBoardConfig()
    A-->>C: *BoardConfiguration (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: AddColumn
    C->>A: AddColumn(title, insertAfterSlug)
    A->>PM: AddColumn(title, insertAfterSlug)
    PM->>PM: Slugify(title), validate uniqueness & reserved names
    PM->>PA: GetBoardConfiguration()
    PM->>PM: Find insertion position, validate bookends
    PM->>PM: Insert new ColumnDefinition (type=doing)
    PM->>PA: EnsureStatusDirectory(slug)
    PA->>PA: os.MkdirAll(tasks/{slug})
    PM->>PA: SaveBoardConfiguration(config)
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(board_config.json)
    PM->>PA: CommitAll("Add column: X")
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(".") -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: *BoardConfiguration
    A-->>C: *BoardConfiguration (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: RemoveColumn
    C->>A: RemoveColumn(slug)
    A->>PM: RemoveColumn(slug)
    PM->>PA: GetBoardConfiguration()
    PM->>PM: Validate column exists, type=doing, no tasks
    PM->>PA: GetTasksByStatus(slug) [verify empty]
    PM->>PA: RemoveStatusDirectory(slug)
    PA->>PA: os.Remove(tasks/{slug})
    PM->>PA: LoadTaskOrder() -> delete zone -> WriteTaskOrder()
    PM->>PM: Remove column from config
    PM->>PA: SaveBoardConfiguration(config)
    PM->>PA: CommitAll("Remove column: X")
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(".") -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: *BoardConfiguration
    A-->>C: *BoardConfiguration (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: RenameColumn
    C->>A: RenameColumn(oldSlug, newTitle)
    A->>PM: RenameColumn(oldSlug, newTitle)
    PM->>PM: Slugify(newTitle), validate uniqueness
    alt Slug unchanged (title-only change)
        PM->>PA: GetBoardConfiguration()
        PM->>PM: Update title in config
        PM->>PA: SaveBoardConfiguration(config)
        PM->>PA: CommitAll("Rename column title")
    else Slug changed
        PM->>PA: RenameStatusDirectory(oldSlug, newSlug)
        PA->>PA: os.Rename(tasks/{old}, tasks/{new})
        PM->>PA: LoadTaskOrder() -> migrate zone key -> WriteTaskOrder()
        PM->>PA: SaveBoardConfiguration(config)
        PM->>PA: CommitAll("Rename column: old -> new")
        PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(".") -> Commit()
    end
    PM-->>A: *BoardConfiguration
    A-->>C: *BoardConfiguration (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: ReorderColumns
    C->>A: ReorderColumns(slugs)
    A->>PM: ReorderColumns(slugs)
    PM->>PA: GetBoardConfiguration()
    PM->>PM: Validate all slugs present, no duplicates
    PM->>PM: Validate bookends (first=todo, last=done)
    PM->>PA: SaveBoardConfiguration(reorderedConfig)
    PM->>PA: CommitAll("Reorder columns")
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(".") -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: *BoardConfiguration
    A-->>C: *BoardConfiguration (Wails DTO)
